Tarkrîp Fight-masters and Brawlers can be found in Nan Wathren in the southern North Downs.

You should defeat Fight-masters and Brawlers, for they awaits battle with any who dare set foot in Nan Wathren uninvited.

<rgb=#FF0000>Fellowship Recommended.</rgb>
You have answered the challenge of the Tarkrîp fighters in central Nan Wathren, besting these terrible foes.

Raging Tarkrîps, Tarkrîp Marksmen, and Tarkrîp Fight-masters can be found in central Nan Wathren.\n\nYou should defeat several of these vicious Orcs in Nan Wathren.
Venturing deeper into Nan Wathren has revealed even stronger breeds of Tarkrîp Orcs.
